@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<div class="card shadow-sm p-4">
    <h2 class="mb-3 text-primary">About MediLink</h2>

    <p>
        MediLink is a healthcare management platform that connects patients, doctors, and administrators
        in one easy-to-use system. It is designed to improve communication and make healthcare services
        more organized and efficient.
    </p>

    <p>
        Patients can view doctors, book and manage appointments, and access their healthcare information
        conveniently. Doctors can manage their schedules and appointments, helping them save time and
        focus on patient care.
    </p>

    <p>
        Administrators can oversee operations, manage users, and ensure the system runs smoothly.
        MediLink focuses on usability, accessibility, and providing a simple, reliable healthcare
        management experience.
    </p>
</div>